Package: cluster.explorer
Title: Interactive Cluster Explorer for Neuroimaging Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Bradley", "Buchsbaum", , "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1108-4866"))
Description: Provides an interactive Shiny application for exploring
    statistical clusters in neuroimaging data. Supports volumetric and
    surface-based visualisation, atlas-annotated cluster tables, design
    variable plots, and extensible analysis plugins. The computation
    engine has zero Shiny dependencies and can be used programmatically.
